            <p>All Tulip wanted was to go to coding camp in Wisconsin. But a scheduling conflict with her parents leads to her attempting the journey herself. Upon encountering the Infinity Train, which presents a ride to Wisconsin, she boards the train and finds herself in a world of possibilities. Now with the help of a white spherical robot named One-One and Atticus, King of the Corgis, Tulip starts her journey to the front of the train. Will she convince the conductor to let her leave the train, and will she discover the purpose of the number on her hand in her mission to escape?</p>
