            <p>Grace and Simon have been enjoying their time on the train. From close friends to leaders of a gang of children called ‘The Apex’, the two of them have been causing havoc on the train for the past couple of years. But one day while leading a raid on the Unfinished Car they get separated from their crew when the false conductor intervenes. Grace and Simon must now travel through a vast number of cars to return to their gang. During their journey they meet Hazel and her denizen Tuba who they hope to introduce to the Apex. But will they make it back, and what trials does the train have in store for their journey?</p>
