            <p>Ryan and Min-Gi were childhood friends with the dream of starting a band together and touring the world. But when Ryan decides that they should leave immediately on tour after graduation,  Min-Gi panics and abandons him. After spending a couple of years apart, Ryan visits Min-Gi trying to convince him to finally go on tour with him. But when Min-Gi refuses, Ryan steals his work keys and soon enough they both find themselves on the Infinity Train. Will they learn to cooperate and reconcile their friendship so they can escape the train?</p>
