            <h3>Book 5 and Beyond</h3>
            <p>While Infinity Train was canceled after Book 4, the crew planned 8 total seasons, potentially including a movie. Book 5 would focus on the character Amelia, her time on the train, and her long term consequences. One of the reasons the show was potentially canceled was that Amelia, an adult character, wouldn’t be relatable to children. Emotional maturity and how characters deal with their struggles is the main focus of Infinity Train which is important for young viewers to learn. Many fans hope that Infinity Train will be renewed through efforts to raise awareness of the show and its incredible storytelling.</p>
